title: Will to Power Journey Home NEW UPLOAD 320kbps
description:
[This is a hopefully more successful torrent of this CD. After 24 hours it still wouldn't seed, which actually turned out to be a good thing--one of the mp3 files was messed up. I've requested that the first be removed.]
I loved listening to this CD in the early 90s, went looking for it the other day and couldn't find it. Sadly, it's stuck at 99.7% on Pirate Bay and, it looks like, everywhere else. So, unable to find a complete copy, I used Soundflower to copy from an Internet streaming service into Audacity and encode the music into 320kbps mp3 audio. I hope you enjoy it...PLEASE SEED!
